1
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:31,879
I'm fine.

2
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,639
We're now at Langxing Wan.

3
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,319
Heading north from Langxing Wan,

4
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,080
we'll arrive in about a day.

5
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,599
Marching into Lingzhou with such fanfare

6
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,280
might tip off the enemy.

7
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,120
Tipping them off is unavoidable.

8
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,199
Lao Gao, Lao Feng.

9
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:19,319
Once we disembark, we'll split up.

10
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,759
Lao Pan and I will disembark first to stall them.

11
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:24,240
You two follow my new route

12
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,400
straight to Yang'an County.

13
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,439
Lao Feng.

14
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,159
Take some men and secure Ya County.

15
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,319
Do not disturb the people.

16
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:30,919
Got it.

17
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,439
Lao Gao.

18
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,879
You'll quietly block the roads.

19
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,080
Don't let word get out.

20
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:34,759
Understood.

21
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:35,719
Chen.

22
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,280
By the sound of it,

23
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,159
you suspect the magistrate of Yang'an County.

24
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,919
Just taking precautions.

25
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:46,800
They might be harboring bandits for profit.

26
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,039
Greetings, General Ning.

27
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,479
My lords.

28
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,360
I am Zhang Yuancang, Prefect of Lingzhou.

29
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:04,599
Welcome, General Ning.

30
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,439
You know me?

31
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,400
You're a prodigy of your generation,

32
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,840
renowned throughout the land.

33
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,319
I've long heard of your name.

34
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,599
You've come by imperial decree to quell the bandits,

35
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:15,599
ridding Lingzhou of its gravest menace,

36
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:17,160
and safeguarding our people.

37
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,920
I have no way to repay you,

38
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,120
so I've prepared some humble wine.

39
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:22,160
I hope the General won't refuse.

40
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:25,439
Very well.

41
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,199
These past few days on the boat,

42
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,639
we've been eating fish every day.

43
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,560
I'm so sick of it I could puke.

44
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:34,199
Indeed.

45
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,959
Time for something new.

46
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,680
The General jests.

47
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:40,079
You've come from afar,

48
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:42,399
so I've prepared local specialties.

49
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,360
Local dishes, eh?

50
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,120
Good. I like that.

51
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,000
Lead the way.

52
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,879
General Ning, after you.

53
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,079
Lord Zhang, please.

54
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:51,639
Quickly now.

55
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,600
Lingzhou really is a fine place.

56
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,600
I'm in a good mood today.

57
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,399
Let's all have a drink!

58
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,720
Cheers! Yes, cheers!

59
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,560
Come, my lords.

60
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:13,759
General Ning,

61
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:16,360
Lingzhou can't compare to the capital.

62
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,319
I hope you'll bear with us.

63
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,720
I have specially prepared for you

64
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:23,360
the White Spirit Fish, a Lingzhou specialty.

65
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,199
I hope it pleases the General.

66
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,199
Fish again?

67
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,279
I've eaten fish the entire way here.

68
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:31,839
Lord Zhang,

69
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,360
bring another dish.

70
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,720
Don't be hasty, General.

71
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:41,279
A taste won't hurt.

72
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,560
Well then,

73
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:51,079
I'd better give it a proper try.

74
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,720
Greetings, General Ning.

75
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,160
So this is what Lord Zhang meant by

76
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,839
Lingzhou's local specialty,

77
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,160
the White Spirit Fish, my lord.

78
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,040
Truly,

79
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:20,319
flawless as white jade,

80
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,360
with spirit and grace.

81
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,079
The General has such a way with words.

82
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,199
Then tonight,

83
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,920
let these little fish

84
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,480
swim into your chamber for a while.

85
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,360
Here in Lingzhou,

86
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:37,199
I've long heard of General Ning's renown.

87
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:38,360
To meet you today,

88
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,600
is the blessing of three lifetimes.

89
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,959
General Ning is so brilliantly talented,

90
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,920
master of both pen and sword,

91
00:06:44,079 --> 00:06:45,360
and so handsome too.

92
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,199
My heart is just melting away.

93
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,000
Don't believe me? Feel for yourself.

94
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,639
General Ning is so well-built.

95
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,439
Such a build,

96
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,839
just looking at you, I'm smitten.

97
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,839
General Ning,

98
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,720
you'd better take

99
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,040
responsibility for me.

100
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:11,120
This general is gifted by nature,

101
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,639
but I only fancy

102
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,879
women from Jiangnan.

103
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,279
So as for you,

104
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,959
someone like you,

105
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:22,439
is more to Lord Zhang's taste.

106
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,639
Well...

107
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,959
You flatter me, you flatter me.

108
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:26,720
Come, come, come.

109
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,360
Let's all toast General Ning together.

110
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,319
Wonderful.

111
00:07:31,079 --> 00:07:31,839
Come on, come on.

112
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,399
Lingzhou really is a fine place.

113
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,360
It was worth the trip.

114
00:07:36,439 --> 00:07:36,920
Cheers.

115
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,319
Here.

116
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,000
I'll drink to you.

117
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,240
Let me serve you well.

118
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,399
General Ning,

119
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,439
don't fight with me over her.

120
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,000
Here.

121
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,279
Please, General.

122
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,560
Let's have another round.

123
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,279
Come, come, come.

124
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:47,839
My lord.

125
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,839
General Ning, here's to you.

126
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:50,720
Oh, by the way,

127
00:07:51,319 --> 00:07:52,800
let me introduce someone to you all.

128
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,519
This man here

129
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,800
is my closest brother,

130
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:57,959
Pan Jinyi.

131
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,319
A true paragon among men,

132
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,360
the finest of our generation.

133
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,519
I'll trouble all of you

134
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,199
to keep him well entertained.

135
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,959
As for me,

136
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,199
I need to relieve myself first.

137
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,319
What are you all standing there for?

138
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,360
Hurry and accompany the General.

139
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,439
General Ning, General Ning.

140
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,360
With so many eyes watching,

141
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,439
I wouldn't be able to go anyway.

142
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,040
Keep him entertained.

143
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,959
I love fish.

144
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,720
Come, I toast all you lords.

145
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,360
Come, come.

146
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:27,079
Lord Pan.

147
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:27,920
Pan Jinyi, Pan Jinyi.

148
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,959
Today's catch is limited.

149
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,480
No, no, no.

150
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,720
We should save a couple for the General.

151
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,560
I'll eat first.

152
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,120
No, wait...

153
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,480
Lord Jiang.

154
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:38,879
What are you doing?

155
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,639
I am Jiang Zhengyang, Governor of Lingzhou.

156
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,679
Greetings, General Ning.

157
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,480
I do not enjoy drinking.

158
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,840
I sought a quiet place to clear my mind.

159
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,320
I have been observing you all along.

160
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,120
As Governor of Lingzhou,

161
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:55,039
your authority equals that of the Prefect.

162
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,799
Yet you wear shabby, tattered clothes.

163
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,200
And there's dirt under your nails.

164
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,960
The result of long-term labor, no doubt.

165
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,279
You're different from those corrupt officials inside.

166
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,320
You

167
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,759
are a good man.

168
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,960
This humble official is dull-witted.

169
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,679
I do not understand what General Ning means.

170
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,919
Has Lord Jiang forgotten

171
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,919
that I am from the Inspectorate?

172
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,840
Once inside the Inspectorate's dungeon,

173
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,840
no mouth remains shut.

174
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,279
Is General Ning intending to frame me

175
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,639
and abuse his authority?

176
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,960
We're both clever men.

177
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,000
Why play games?

178
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:35,679
You saw me acting the playboy in there,

179
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,799
but that was merely putting on a show.

180
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,200
General Ning earlier

181
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,039
did not seem to be pretending.

182
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,279
Forgotten how I beheaded the Empress's brother?

183
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,759
My purpose in coming here

184
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,879
is the matter of Lingzhou's bandit scourge.

185
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,679
First, let me ask you a question.

186
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:52,039
Lingzhou has seven counties in total.

187
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:54,080
Why is only Yang'an County plagued by bandits?

188
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,399
It seems the General came well-prepared.

189
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:57,799
I bear His Majesty's mandate.

190
00:09:58,399 --> 00:10:00,600
Suppressing these bandits is imperative.

191
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,039
Yang'an County is ringed by tall mountains and dense forests,

192
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,639
ideal terrain for bandits to hide.

193
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,279
Suppression is therefore more difficult.

194
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,240
I'm aware of that, Lord Jiang.

195
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,559
I'm from Longevity Village in Yang'an County.

196
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,559
I'm here by imperial decree to suppress the bandits.

197
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:15,840
If I do not eliminate those outlaws,

198
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,879
I will not leave Lingzhou.

199
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:19,519
Lord Jiang,

200
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,440
tell me something useful.

201
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,360
Then I shall take this gamble.

202
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,240
Please accept my bow, General.

203
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,120
No need to kneel.

204
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:33,000
Let's stand up and speak.

205
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,440
Please.

206
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,000
According to my covert investigation,

207
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,240
the bandits in Yang'an appeared suddenly.

208
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:45,039
They seem driven by some specific purpose.

209
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,159
They only raid Longevity Village in Yang'an County.

210
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,279
The authorities have sent troops repeatedly,

211
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,360
with little effect.

212
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:52,039
Yet vast sums of silver have been spent.

213
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,720
You mean they harbor bandits to enrich themselves?

214
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,159
Suppressing bandits requires silver.

215
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:57,000
But where does that silver come from?

216
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,759
Naturally, from the common people.

217
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:00,919
Now in every county of Lingzhou,

218
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,799
a new levy has appeared,

219
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,200
called the Bandit Suppression Tax.

220
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,639
Bandit Suppression Tax?

221
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:08,960
In Yang'an County alone,

222
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,679
the tax collected in a single month

223
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,039
amounts to tens of thousands of taels.

224
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,519
Yet the expenditure of this silver

225
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,080
has no clear records.

226
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,000
They merely claim it's for bandit suppression.

227
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,679
Don't the people have any grievances?

228
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,360
What good would grievances do?

229
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:24,679
I have submitted memorials to the court many times,

230
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,960
but they all went unanswered.

231
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,039
Lord Jiang,

232
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,200
as Governor,

233
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,519
you have the right to an audience with His Majesty.

234
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,679
Why not go to the capital and petition him?

235
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,799
I do not fear for my own life.

236
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,000
But I have elderly parents

237
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:43,480
and young children to care for.

238
00:11:47,759 --> 00:11:49,080
I have one more lead.

239
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,679
Over these years,

240
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,440
I knew this matter was far from simple.

241
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,639
So I secretly sent trusted men to investigate.

242
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:57,960
They found that in the mountains of Longevity Village,

243
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,000
those men are digging for something.

244
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,440
And felling trees by the river.

245
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:02,879
I truly wished to uncover this matter.

246
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,159
But alas,

247
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,759
my authority as Governor has long been stripped away.

248
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,600
The officials and bandits are in cahoots.

249
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:11,000
I am truly powerless to act.

250
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,799
This is the location of their logging camp.

251
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:26,799
Digging in the mountains,

252
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,039
and felling trees by the river.

253
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,960
There's definitely something fishy going on.

254
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:33,879
General.

255
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,639
This matter is far from simple.

256
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,919
Please proceed with caution, General.
